						               													<description>An onset-and-rimes spelling card game with Crazy Eights mechanics.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The deck has: &amp;#10;- 41 Building block word cards, each with an onset [1-2 consonant word start] at the top of the card and a rime [word ending of a vowel and following consonants] at the bottom.&amp;#10;- 8 Star option cards, each with 6 different onsets, one of which is starred.&amp;#10;- 7 You Lose! cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During their turn a player plays a card with an onset that can go with a rime of the card on top of the discard pile to make a valid word. If they cannot play any card they draw a card and end their turn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The You Lose! card makes the next player draw two cards and otherwise skip their turn.  To win the hand, a player must play a You Lose! card as their final card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
